\v 4 Ngubani ongaveza okuhlambulukileyo kokungcolileyo\x + 15.14. Joha. 3.6. Hlab. 51.5.\x*? Kakho loyedwa\x + Hlab. 14.3.\x*.
\v 5 Lokhu insuku zakhe zimisiwe, inani lenyanga zakhe likuwe, ummisele imingcele yakhe angeyedlule\x + 14.5.\x*;
