\v 7 Ngoba kukhona ithemba esihlahleni uba siganyulwa\x + 14.14.\x* ukuthi sizabuya sihlume\x + 29.20. 14.14.\x*, lokuthi ihlumela laso kaliyikuphela\x + 8.16.\x*.
