\v 10 Kodwa umuntu uyafa alaliswe phansi\x + Hlab. 88.4,5.\x*, yebo, umuntu uyaphela, ungaphi-ke\x + 20.7.\x*?
\v 11 Amanzi ayemuka elwandle\x + Isa. 19.5.\x*, lomfula uyoma utshe\x + Isa. 19.5.\x*,
\v 12 ngokunjalo umuntu uyalala phansi angavuki; kuze kuthi amazulu angabikho, bangavuki, kumbe bangaphatshanyiswa ebuthongweni babo\x + Hlab. 72.7. Dute. 11.21. Hlab. 89.29. 148.4-6. Jer. 31.35,36. Hlab. 102.26.\x*.
