\v 13 Kungathi ungangifihla engcwabeni\x + Hlab. 27.5. 31.20.\x*, ungithukuze\x + Hlab. 27.5. 31.20.\x*, ize iphenduke intukuthelo yakho\x + 9.13. Isa. 26.20.\x*, ungimisele isikhathi esimisiweyo, ungikhumbule\x + 14.5.\x*!
\v 14 Uba umuntu esifa, uzabuya aphile yini\x + Hlab. 89.48.\x*? Zonke insuku zemfazo yami\x + 7.1.\x* ngizalinda\x + 13.15.\x*, kuze kufike ukukhululwa kwami\x + 14.7.\x*.
\v 15 Uzabiza, mina-ke ngizasabela\x + 13.22.\x*, uzalangatha umsebenzi wezandla zakho\x + 10.3.\x*.
