\v 21 Amadodana akhe ayadunyiswa\x + Jer. 30.19.\x*, kodwa engakwazi\x + Tshu. 9.5.\x*; kumbe ayehliselwa phansi, kodwa angakunanzeleli\x + Jer. 30.19.\x*.
\v 22 Kodwa inyama yakhe kuye isebuhlungwini, lomphefumulo wakhe kuye uyalila.